This button opens the menu with all the options to share and print your design.
The main navigation contains buttons for document level options. To switch between buttons, use the left and right keys and to activate, press Enter. To skip to the canvas, press "⌘F2".
Canvas

We’ve locked your design while you publish your website.

The canvas is where your design is. To navigate into the page, press Enter. To navigate into groups or elements on the page, press Enter again. Press tab to move to the next page, group, or element. To operate the toolbar, use the "⌘F1" key. If an element is selected, move it using the arrow keys; rotate using the "," key and "." key; and resize using the arrow keys with the "⌘" key. All of these keys can be modified with the "⇧" key to increase increment.

Class

Carnatic music is a genre of Indian
classical music that has been around
for centuries and is still popular today.
To learn more, people can visit the
website and take courses ranging from
basic introductory to advanced. These
courses cover topics such as the basics
of Carnatic music, learning to play
instruments, and exploring ragas and
talas.

I recently had the opportunity to
take classes at Divine Swarams
– a Carnatic vocal class located

made learning Carnatic music
accessible yet challenging. We covered

The instructors were knowledgeable and
patient, which helped me to develop my
understanding of Carnatic music.

Randelo Co.
